quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  12,43,"Laam…óo on wi'i: \"Min mi yi'ii (e koy…óol) na'i jee…ói…ói fay…ói, na nyaama foo∆¥u…ói jee…ói…ói …óin, e dukke jee…ói…ói kecce, e go…ó…ói goo yooru…ói. Ko onon yo dental, firtanee lam ngol koy…óol am, si on laatike firtoo…ìe koy…ói"
  12,44,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko jii…ìu-jaa…ìu koy…ói ! Men wonaali anndu…ìe firo koy…ói"
  12,45,"Da…óu…óo on e …ìeya …ói…óo miijitii …ìaawo dumunna o wi'i: \"Min mi humpitay on firo maggol. Nulee lam"
  12,46,"Yuusufu, an yo goongu…óo! Yeetii men fii na'i jee…ói…ói fay…ói, na nyaama foo∆¥u…ói jee…ói…ói …óin, e dukke jee…ói…ói kecce, e go…ó…ói goo yooru…ói, belajo'o mi ruttoo ka yim…ìe …ìen, belajo'o, …ìe annday"
  12,47,"O maaki: \"On remay duu…ói jee…ói…ói jokkondir…ói. Kala ko so√±u…óon, accon …óum ka dukkal(butaali) mun, si wanaa see…óa e kon ko √±aamoton"
  12,48,"Refti aroyay …ìaawo …óum, duu…ìi jee…ói…ói sa…ótu…ói, …óin (duu…ìi) no √±aama kon ko marna…óon …ói si wanaa see…óa e ko maroton [fii awdi]"
  12,49,"Refti aroya …ìaawo …óum, hitaande, ko e mayre yim…ìe …ìen to…ìetee, ko e mayre kadi …ìe hamata"